<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>PulseHub | For Creators, by Creators</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Poppins:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #0a0c17;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      background: #121423;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 158, 235, 0.1);
    }

    .logo {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 3V5M12 19V21M3 12H5M19 12H21M5 3C5 3 7 10 12 10C17 10 19 3 19 3M5 3C5 3 7 17 12 17C17 17 19 3 19 3" stroke="%236d9eeb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M12 10V14" stroke="%236d9eeb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2" fill="%236d9eeb"/><circle cx="12" cy="14" r="2" fill="%236d9eeb"/></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
      background-color: transparent;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .logo:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6d9eeb;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      position: relative;
    }

    h1::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6d9eeb, #a084ff);
      border-radius: 1px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #ccc;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #ddd;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 28px;
    }

    li::before {
      content: 'âœ¨';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      color: #6d9eeb;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: white;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6d9eeb, #a084ff);
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(109, 158, 235, 0.3);
    }

    .btn svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      margin-right: 8px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo"></div>
    <h1>PulseHub</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A premium community for content creators, streamers, and digital artists. Collaborate. Grow. Thrive.</p>
    <p class="tagline">Where creativity meets connection</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Network with top creators & collaborate on projects</li>
      <li>Get early access to tools, templates, and resources</li>
      <li>Exclusive AMAs, feedback sessions, and growth workshops</li>
      <li>Safe space to share ideas, without the noise</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="/signup" class="btn">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
        <path d="M12 4v16m-8-8h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      Join the Waitlist
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
